  "A stock is priced at $120 with an annual dividend of $4.80. If the stock price drops to $96, what happens to the dividend yield (assuming the dividend stays the same)?": "",
  "Yield decreases from 4% to 3%": "",
  "Yield increases from 4% to 5%": "",
  "Yield increases from 4% to 8%": "",
